{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Visit_to_Dreven",
  "title": "A Visit to Dreven",
  "summary": "Arriving at the Admiral Bevven Spaceport on the Imperial world Dreven aboard the shuttle Crazy Diamond, the cold and confident Sabbathius Osbourne and his companion -- introduced as Simone Drake but operating as Piper -- are met by their escorts, Agent Ramsey and the imperious IntSec Director Drocal Arconen. Drocal leads them down through the spaceport's elevators into an interrogation chamber, where a tense battle of wills unfolds: Sabbath, a former Imperial admiral long absent from the Empire, demands an audience with Grand Moff Ariak Caldny by the will of the Emperor himself, while Drocal scorns his insolence and questions his claims. When the enraged Director takes Ramsey's blaster and gestures threateningly toward Piper, Sabbath coldly warns that killing her would bring fatal consequences from the CSA. Intrigued and unsettled by Sabbath's invocation of the true Emperor Palpatine, Drocal relents, agreeing to let him meet Caldny the following evening to prove his claims -- under the certainty that any deception will mean termination -- before the pair retire to their ship.",
